{"tid":1155181,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎一齊分享下你幻想中既未來會係點","createTime":"2019-05-14T19:11:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T19:15:06.000Z","uid":200002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"33dcbce6f9d8844b609baa4f587e85e454bd4c80","tid":1155181,"uid":200002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T19:11:12.000Z","msg":"相信大家由細到大都對自己既未來好多幻想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如職業 生活 <br />\n大家既然入咗黎<br />\n不如分享下你細個/而家幻想未來既自己<br />\n會變成點/會做緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以後再返黎/而家 睇下你有冇成為你幻想中既人<br />\np.s.純粹訓唔著 攤係床度就容易幻想未來<br />\n<br />\n想知道大家幻想過既未來會係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如我:<br />\n幻想過同中學開始既男朋友<br />\n同一間大學 同一科 然後同一個地方返工 會結婚 日日見 <br />\n生一個小朋友 不論男女連名都諗好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放工可以拖住手周圍去 即使結咗婚仍然好似熱戀期咁<br />\n到七老八十仲可以sweet住過落去 你笑下我 我玩下你咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現實：真係同一間大學同一科啊 不過冇然後了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幻想與現實總是有點落差<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d12df6ccd1f78a829d315dd562b66840af5926f","tid":1155181,"uid":200002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T19:14:13.000Z","msg":"up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2110efe2b6e8b8d351d20661d3ecde67cb5aa903","tid":1155181,"uid":200002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T19:14:24.000Z","msg":"up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b89e09b3ff38cf66fdcd34a826c125c88535f46","tid":1155181,"uid":236676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T19:15:06.000Z","msg":"善"}]}